Data Visualization Demonstration

Histogram

ggplot(data=diamonds, aes(x=carat)) +
  geom_histogram(
    #aes(fill=clarity), 
    bins=30
    ) + 
  ggtitle("Distribution of diamond sizes")

Scatter plots and Line plots

ggplot(data=mpg, aes(x=hwy, y=displ)) +
  geom_point(position="jitter") + 
  geom_smooth(
    method=lm, se=FALSE
    )
